.name
PanicSociety
.fullname
Escape from the Panic Society
.type
Role Playing
.short
Multilevel graphic puzzle adventure.
.description
Update to version 1.0
Hillery and her Liberals friends have taken total control of the
world. You are one of some 10 million people left, scheduled for
transfering to the country of your origin. But, someone has
tampered with your environmental control causing you to awaken
from a mind controlled state. Your objective, to learn all you
can about Panic Society, escape from your prison, find master
control, shut it down, and rebuild society.
Panic Society uses the mouse and keyboard.
.version
1.1
.date
1995.4.30
.author
Ronald F. Picardi
630 Bacon Rd.
Saginaw, MI 48609
.restrictions
Level 1 not intended for young children due to written references
of sex, violence, and race. (Hey, it has all been on TV or in the 
print media anyhow.) Game will look for level 2 when you find the
exit.
.requirements
Any amiga with 1 meg or more ram
Requires narrator.device, speak-handler and translator.library
